  <title>fdk-aac-&fdk-aac-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      fdk-aac package provides the Fraunhofer FDK AAC library, which is
      purported to be a high quality Advanced Audio Coding implementation.
    </para>

